works.title: Face Generation from Textual Features using Conditionally Trained Inputs to Generative Adversarial Networks
works.abstract: Generative Networks have proved to be extremely effective in image restoration and reconstruction in the past few years. Generating faces from textual descriptions is one such application where the power of generative algorithms can be used.
